<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٧٩ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا إِسْمَاعِيلُ قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنِي مَالِكٌ، عَنْ ابْنِ شِهَابٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ <span class="special">﵁</span>:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَنّ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> دَخَلَ عَامَ الْفَتْحِ وَعَلَى رَأْسِهِ الْمِغْفَرُ، فَلَمَّا نَزَعَهُ جَاءَ رَجُلٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗١١٠٨⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">فَقَالَ:</span> إِنَّ ابْنَ خَطَلٍ مُتَعَلِّقٌ بِأَسْتَارِ الْكَعْبَةِ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(اقْتُلُوهُ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
